'''''Allium materculae''''' is a species of [[Allium|onion]] native to [[Turkey]], [[Iran]], and [[Russia]].<ref>Fritsch, R.M. & Abbasi, M. (2013). A taxonomic review of ''Allium'' subg. ''Melanocrommyum'' in Iran: 1-240. IPK Gatersleben, Germany.</ref><ref name=enid>[http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/acceptedRef.do?name_id=295996 Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant Families]</ref><ref>[http://www.theplantlist.org/tpl1.1/record/kew-295996 The Plant List, ''Allium materculae'' Bordz.]</ref>

